# Design Token Enforcement

## The Rule: No Magic Numbers

Every style value must come from the theme. No hardcoded pixels, colors, or durations.

## Spacing — Use `theme.spacing[n]`

```ts
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
padding: '16px';
margin: '8px 24px';
gap: '12px';

// ✅ CORRECT — 4-point grid
padding: ${props => props.theme.spacing[4]};   // 16px
margin: ${props => props.theme.spacing[2]} ${props => props.theme.spacing[6]};  // 8px 24px
gap: ${props => props.theme.spacing[3]};       // 12px
```

Valid spacing keys: `0, 0.5, 1, 1.5, 2, 2.5, 3, 3.5, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12, 14, 16, 20, 24, 28, 32, 36, 40, 44, 48, 52, 56, 60, 64, 72, 80, 96`

> **Note**: spacing[50], spacing[100], spacing[150], spacing[176], spacing[300] do NOT exist. Use the nearest valid key.

## Colors — Use `theme.colors.*`

```ts
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
color: '#3b82f6';
background: '#0f172a';

// ✅ CORRECT
color: ${props => props.theme.colors.primary[500]};
background: ${props => props.theme.colors.background};
```

Color palette:
- `primary[50–950]` — blue scale
- `neutral[50–950]` — gray scale
- `background`, `surface`, `text`, `textSecondary`, `textMuted`
- `border`, `divider`
- `hero.text`, `hero.textSecondary`, `hero.textMuted`

> **Note**: `colors.gray` does NOT exist. Use `colors.neutral[n]` instead.

## Typography — Use `theme.typography.*`

```ts
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
font-size: '14px';
font-weight: 600;
font-family: 'Inter, sans-serif';

// ✅ CORRECT
font-size: ${props => props.theme.typography.fontSize.sm};
font-weight: ${props => props.theme.typography.fontWeight.semibold};
font-family: ${props => props.theme.typography.fontFamily.primary};
```

Font sizes: `xs, sm, base, lg, xl, 2xl, 3xl, 4xl, 5xl`
Font weights: `thin, light, normal, medium, semibold, bold, extrabold, black`

## Border Radius — Use `theme.radius.*`

```ts
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
border-radius: '8px';
border-radius: '50%';

// ✅ CORRECT
border-radius: ${props => props.theme.radius.lg};   // 8px
border-radius: ${props => props.theme.radius.full}; // 9999px
```

Radius keys: `none, sm, base, md, lg, xl, 2xl, 3xl, full`

## Shadows — Conditional by Mode

```ts
// In dark/EVA: use depth tokens (not shadow tokens)
// In light: shadow tokens are fine

// ✅ CORRECT for all modes
box-shadow: ${props => props.theme.shadows.lg};

// But in dark/EVA hover states, prefer depth.cardBorderHover
// over adding box-shadow — shadows are all 'none' in dark theme
```

## Z-Index — Use `theme.zIndex.*`

```ts
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
z-index: 9999;
z-index: 100;

// ✅ CORRECT
z-index: ${props => props.theme.zIndex.modal};
z-index: ${props => props.theme.zIndex.dropdown};
```

Z-index keys: `hide, base, raised, dropdown, sticky, overlay, modal, popover, toast, tooltip`

## Transitions — Use `theme.hoverTransition()`

```ts
// ❌ FORBIDDEN
transition: 'all 0.2s ease';

// ✅ CORRECT
${props => props.theme.hoverTransition()};
// or with custom property:
${props => props.theme.hoverTransition('border-color', '0.15s')};
```

## Component Pattern Template

```tsx
const MyCard = styled.div`
  padding: ${props => props.theme.spacing[6]};
  background: ${props => props.theme.colors.surface};
  border: 1px solid ${props => props.theme.depth?.cardBorder ?? props.theme.colors.border};
  border-radius: ${props => props.theme.radius.xl};
  font-family: ${props => props.theme.typography.fontFamily.primary};
  ${props => props.theme.hoverTransition('border-color')};

  &:hover {
    border-color: ${props => props.theme.depth?.cardBorderHover ?? props.theme.colors.primary[500]};
  }
`
```
